1. Install the tailwind dependencies

```
npm install -D tailwindcss
npx tailwindcss init
```

2. In your package.json, set up the correct path. See the path hiearchy in github

```
content: ["./**/*.{html,js}"],
```

3. Create a css folder outside the _hb_officials, call e.g css/main.css

4. Update the package.json file
```
  "tailrun": "npx tailwindcss -i ./tailwind/css/main.css -o ./_hb_official/css/output.css --watch"
```
